quran[5]{c,v,t}:
  13,27,"Abahakanye Imana yabo y’ukuri bavuga bati:- ni kuki atamanuriwe ibitangaro bivuye ku Muremyi wiwe? Wewe vuga uti:- mu vy’ukuri Imana yama ireka umuntu agatakara kugushaka kwayo kandi ikarongora abatumbereye iwe"
  13,28,"Nibarya bemeye Imana yabo y’ukuri n’imitima yabo ikaba ihumuye neza mukwibuka Imana, namwe nimwumvirize neza mukwibuka Imana imitima yabo ihumuye"
  13,29,"Bamwe bemeye Imana yabo y’ukuri nukugira ibikorwa vyiza, umunezero uzoba ari uwabo n’ingaruka nziza"
  13,30,"Uko rero niko twakuzanye mubantu bamaze kuhita imbere yabo n’abandi bantu kugira ngo ubasomere kuvyo twaguhaye, nabo bakaba bahakana nyene Imigisha mininiya wewe vuga uti:- niwe Muremyi wanje kuko ntayindi Mana isengwa atariyo yonyene ikaba ariyo nizeye n’ingaruka yanje nikuriyo"
  13,31,"Iyo haba iyi Qur’ani nyeranda hakaba muriyo imisozi yari gukurwaho canke kuriyoSi yari gusatagurika, canke abitavye Imana yabo bari kuvugishwa, mugabo si uko rero ibintu vyose nivy’Imana, mbega ntibaramenya abemeye Imana yabo y’ukuri yuko Imana iyo ibishaka ntankeka yari kurongora abantu bose, canke ivyago ntibizoreka kubashikira bamwe bahakana Imana yabo y’ukuri kubera ivyo bagize, canke hazomanuka ubu vuba no mubisagara vyabo kugeza aho hazoshika indagano y’Imana, mu vy’ukuri Imana ntita indagano yayo"